NK011(da)005:0: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i dbang gi cho ga jo bo lang lab kyi lugs bzhugs so //
NK011(da)005:1: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)005:2: de nas dbang bskur gral bca' ste //
NK011(da)005:3: dam tshig mna' chu bcas nas ni //
NK011(da)005:4: nang du bos la 'di skad brjod //
NK011(da)005:7: sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam sgo 'di //
NK011(da)005:8: skal ldan khyod la gnyer du dbog pa ni //
NK011(da)005:9: dang po la ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)005:10: de las 'das na mtha' gnyis mun par ltung //
NK011(da)005:11: gnyis pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)005:12: de las 'das na nyan thos sa ru ltung //
NK011(da)005:13: gsum pa la ni sbyor ba'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)005:14: de las 'das na mngal gyi srin bur skye //
NK011(da)005:15: bzhi pa la ni spyod pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)005:16: dngos su spyod na las kyi srin por skye //
NK011(da)005:17: rtsa ba yan lag ji snyed grags pa rnams //
NK011(da)005:18: lta spyod sgrub dang las kyi bye brag gis //
NK011(da)005:19: so so'i rim pa bzhin du bsrung zhes bya //
NK011(da)005:21: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK011(da)005:22: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK011(da)005:23: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK011(da)005:25: +amo sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum dz+ny+aa na sa t+wa a /
NK011(da)005:26: de nas gzhal yas khang sgo phye ste /
NK011(da)005:27: byang chub rjes phur pa'i lha tshogs la //
NK011(da)005:28: mchod chen bgyis pas phur pa'i lhar //
NK011(da)005:29: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:30: phur pa'i lha tshogs bdag la stsol //
NK011(da)005:31: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK011(da)005:32: bdag ni skal ldan bde chen la'o //
NK011(da)005:33: rab dgyes 'phrul la bdag dga' ste //
NK011(da)005:34: bla med byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:35: skal pa bzang la bdag daga'o //
NK011(da)005:37: rig pa'i me tog 'di dor bas //
NK011(da)005:38: sngon tshe bsgrub pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK011(da)005:39: da lta nyid du bdag la 'bab par shog /
NK011(da)005:41: mig dbye de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK011(da)005:42: dkyil 'khor dam pa lta bar gyis //
NK011(da)005:43: sngags dang phyag rgya 'grub par byed //
NK011(da)005:44: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK011(da)005:45: de nas phyag 'tshal bshags pa bya /
NK011(da)005:46: dkyil dkyil 'khor bstan pa 'khor chen po'i rang bzhin ni //
NK011(da)005:47: dbyings las ye shes gsum snang gru gsum ste //
NK011(da)005:48: rtag chad dbu mar mnga' brnyes zla gam gsum //
NK011(da)005:49: 'khor ba rtsad nas bcad phyir 'khor lor bstan //
NK011(da)005:50: spros pa med pa'i tshul gyis kun nas zlum //
NK011(da)005:51: ye shes kun tu rgyas phyir gru chad bzhi //
NK011(da)005:52: 'das dang ma 'das mtshams su bar khyams bstan //
NK011(da)005:53: ye shes lnga lngan thod pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)005:54: rig pa shar sgo yon tan lho yi sgo //
NK011(da)005:55: ma rig nub sgo bag chags byang gi sgo //
NK011(da)005:56: yon tan mi zad sgo khyud rnam thar brgyad //
NK011(da)005:57: rta babs mi phyed rdo rje phreng bas brgyan //
NK011(da)005:58: skal ldan bu yis de ltar shes par gyis //
NK011(da)005:60: tshogs brgyad rnam dag gtso bo'i sku //
NK011(da)005:61: yul ni yum du dag pa ste //
NK011(da)005:62: ngag 'khyal ba dang srog gcod pa //
NK011(da)005:63: phra ma tshig rtsub bzhi po ni //
NK011(da)005:64: phyogs bzhi'i khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)005:65: rdzun dang log lta ma byin len //
NK011(da)005:66: gnod sems rnam par dag pa ni //
NK011(da)005:67: mtshams kyi khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)005:68: 'dod chags brnab sems rnam dag pa //
NK011(da)005:69: steng 'og khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)005:70: de rnams kun gyi yon tan gyi //
NK011(da)005:71: cha rnams rnam dag yum rnams so //
NK011(da)005:72: 'du byed sems kyi tshogs rnams la //
NK011(da)005:73: dad dang 'dun pa la sogs pa //
NK011(da)005:74: rnam par dag pa phra men tshogs //
NK011(da)005:75: sems kyi las rnams 'grub pas na //
NK011(da)005:76: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK011(da)005:77: bdag 'dzin gnyis dang ma bral bas //
NK011(da)005:78: srung ma'i tshogs su bstan pa yin //
NK011(da)005:79: de lta bu yi lha tshogs ni //
NK011(da)005:80: rigs kyi bu yis shes par gyis //
NK011(da)005:81: de nas las kyi bum chu blangs //
NK011(da)005:82: mtshams kyang drag tu bcad byas la //
NK011(da)005:83: rdo rje rnam 'joms brjod bya zhing //
NK011(da)005:84: slob ma'i mgo lus dag par bkru //
NK011(da)005:85: de nas dad ldan slob ma yis //
NK011(da)005:86: bla ma mnyes pa'i yon phul te //
NK011(da)005:87: bzang po'i gos gyon me tog thogs //
NK011(da)005:88: dngos grub 'dod phyir gsol ba gdab //
NK011(da)005:89: rjes thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK011(da)005:90: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK011(da)005:91: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK011(da)005:92: byin rlabs dbang ni bdag la stsol //
NK011(da)005:93: bla mas tshig gsum mthun pa la //
NK011(da)005:94: byin rlabs dbang ni bskur bar bya //
NK011(da)005:95: de ltar brjod la byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)005:96: rdo rje gzhon nu skur bskyed la //
NK011(da)005:97: me tog lha dang bcas pa ni //
NK011(da)005:98: slob ma'i spyir bzhag 'di skad brjod //
NK011(da)005:99: 'di ni khyod kyi byang chub sems //
NK011(da)005:100: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)005:101: bcom ldan 'das dang skal ba gcig /
NK011(da)005:102: byang chub sems ni mngon du bstan //
NK011(da)005:103: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa a +aah /
NK011(da)005:104: chos dbyings yum gyi bum pa na //
NK011(da)005:105: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)005:106: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi chus //
NK011(da)005:107: spyi nas bstim zhing dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:108: k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah da ni lha tshogs kyis dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:109: lha phur rim bzhin bton la bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)005:111: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)005:112: shin tu mi bzad rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK011(da)005:113: zhe sdang thugs mchog rak+sha he ru ka /
NK011(da)005:114: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi lha chen bardzisa //
NK011(da)005:115: 'jigs byed sku la dur khrod rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK011(da)005:116: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs 'jigs byed dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)005:117: yab yum gnyis su med pa yang //
NK011(da)005:118: gsang ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)005:119: bskal pa'i mtha' nas bsnyen bsnyen pa //
NK011(da)005:120: ring ba'i dus nas bsgrub bsgrub pa //
NK011(da)005:121: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i don lags kyi //
NK011(da)005:122: skal ldan rigs kyi bu mchog la //
NK011(da)005:123: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:124: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+aip+ta tsakra ha na a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:125: rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis slob ma khyod la
NK011(da)005:126: dpal rdo rje gzho na nu yab yum gyi dbang
NK011(da)005:127: bskur bas lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa rnam
NK011(da)005:128: par dag nas / sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar dbyer mi phyed par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:129: dbang phyug khro bo'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:131: za byed rngams pa mche ba gtsigs pa las //
NK011(da)005:132: khro bo'i za byed rngams pa'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros //
NK011(da)005:133: zhal gyi hom khung thig le dmar po nas //
NK011(da)005:134: ye shes khro bo mang po sprul pa'i tshogs //
NK011(da)005:135: khams gsum thal bar rlog pa'i las mdzad pa //
NK011(da)005:136: ye shes khro bo bcu yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:137: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:138: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum a b+hi n+ai
NK011(da)005:139: la dan+da ya man+ta ka +aar+ya ya tsa la h+ya
NK011(da)005:140: g+r+ai wa h+aum a par dzi ta a mri ta
NK011(da)005:141: kun+da li tree lo kya bi dza ya ma h+aa
NK011(da)005:142: b+aa la h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:144: khro bo chen po bcu'i dbang bskur bas stobs bcu'i stobs su gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:145: dbang bcu sku la rdzogs pas phyogs bcu'i dregs pa
NK011(da)005:146: can mang po 'dus shing rin po che'i lo ka
NK011(da)005:147: brdal ba'i mthu stobs dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:149: khro rgyal sku la gnyis med sbyor ba mo //
NK011(da)005:150: srin po'i mgo dang srin mo'i ral pa can //
NK011(da)005:151: sprul pa'i pho nya ci bgyi khro mo'i tshogs //
NK011(da)005:152: lha srin mang po 'dul ba'i rtags su byung //
NK011(da)005:153: ye shes khro mo bcu yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:154: badz+ra rak+sha ya ti h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:155: khro bo bcu'i dbang bskur bas sprul pa'i pho nya
NK011(da)005:156: mang po dbyings nas bton nas mi mthun dgra bgegs
NK011(da)005:157: rdul du rlog pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par
NK011(da)005:158: gyur cig / phra thabs nyi shu'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:159: phra men tshogs dang sbyor ba'i byin rlabs dang //
NK011(da)005:160: 'dul byed sprul pa 'byung ba'i byin rlabs ni //
NK011(da)005:161: ral pa kham nag rdo rje'i mche ba can //
NK011(da)005:162: ro la rngams pa ti ra 'brad pa dang //
NK011(da)005:163: zhag la rngams shing rus pa 'cha' ba'i tshul //
NK011(da)005:164: stag g.yag sha ba gzig gi mgo //
NK011(da)005:165: byi la spyang ki seng ge'i mgo //
NK011(da)005:166: dom dred phag gi mgo can dang //
NK011(da)005:167: bya rgod bya rog 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK011(da)005:168: khwa ta pu shud khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)005:169: pha wang sre mong byi ba'i mgo //
NK011(da)005:170: smig bu'i mog can pra men tshogs //
NK011(da)005:171: 'dab chags khrag 'thung sder mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK011(da)005:172: stong gsum zad par bsgral yang tshim pa med //
NK011(da)005:173: khams gsum yongs sgrol mdzad kyang tshim pa med //
NK011(da)005:174: za byed rngams pa'i tshogs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:175: badz+ra u ka ra mu ka h+aum /
NK011(da)005:176: badz+ra hu sho ka mu kha h+aum /
NK011(da)005:178: phra men mgo brnyan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum
NK011(da)005:179: yongs bsgral mdzad pa 'gug byed pho nya'i dbang dang
NK011(da)005:181: phur pa rdzas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)005:182: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)005:183: yon tan rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)005:184: mi g.yo chos mchog sku gsung thugs kyi bdag /
NK011(da)005:185: sdug bsngal 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK011(da)005:186: thugs rjes dbyer med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK011(da)005:187: khro rgyal 'bar ba sid+d+hi'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:188: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:189: phur pa'i dbang bskur bas las rnam bzhi brtsams pa
NK011(da)005:190: tsam gyis 'grub pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK011(da)005:191: / sgo ma bzhi'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:192: byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms tshul //
NK011(da)005:193: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra 'dul zhing //
NK011(da)005:194: gzhal yas phyogs bzhi ye shes lnga yi ngang //
NK011(da)005:195: tshad med bzhi yi ye shes 'dul la mkhas //
NK011(da)005:196: phrin las rnam bzhi'i ye shesadabanga sbyin no //
NK011(da)005:197: dzahh+aum bam hoh a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:198: sgo ma bzhi'i dbang bskur bas ye shes bzhi'i rig
NK011(da)005:199: pa nang nas shar nas tshad med pa bzhi'i phrin
NK011(da)005:200: las te las rnams ji ltar dmigs pa tsam gyis
NK011(da)005:202: phur bu'i srung ma'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:203: shwa na bdag nyid bswe mo srung ma'i tshogs //
NK011(da)005:204: sprul pa'i pho nya bswe gdong mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)005:205: ci bcol las byed pho nya mang po'i tshogs //
NK011(da)005:206: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i sta gon ye nas mdzad //
NK011(da)005:207: rtsal gyi khyad par dpag gis mi nus pa //
NK011(da)005:208: sprul pas gang la ci 'dul phrin las mdzad //
NK011(da)005:209: sprul pa sna tshogs mang po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:212: pho nya 'bum phrag mang po'i dbang bskur bas las
NK011(da)005:213: bzhi la sogs pa bya'o 'tshal bzhed pa tsam la
NK011(da)005:214: rag las te ji ltar dmigs pa'i sprul pa las
NK011(da)005:215: la 'gyed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:216: sgom sgrub kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)005:217: slob ma'i lus ngag yid gsum rdo rje gzhon nu
NK011(da)005:218: dang dbyer med par byas nas lag tu sngags phur
NK011(da)005:220: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)005:221: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK011(da)005:222: srid gsum phur pa'i rang bzhin du //
NK011(da)005:223: bsgom zhing sgrub pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:224: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:225: sngags phur chen po lag tu byin te dbang bskur
NK011(da)005:226: bas srid pa gsum ka phur bu'i skur rtogs nas
NK011(da)005:227: / dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer med par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:229: chos nyid bdud rtsi chos kyi char //
NK011(da)005:230: skal ldan 'di la dbab pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:231: mthun par sngags bsgrag chos kyi dbang //
NK011(da)005:232: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK011(da)005:233: lam h+aum d+harma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:234: d+harma lag tu gtad de dbang bskur bas chos nyid
NK011(da)005:235: kyi don rtogs shing 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK011(da)005:236: par gyur cig / de nas phur pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)005:237: rdo rje rab tu k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)005:238: yum bzhi phyag rgya byin brlabs nas //
NK011(da)005:239: khyod kyi lag tu 'di byin pas //
NK011(da)005:240: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:241: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan mo ha g+ha
NK011(da)005:242: ta ya b+ha ga w+aa na h+r+ai sh+ti bi ti
NK011(da)005:243: badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la
NK011(da)005:244: ya dzahh+aum bam hoh sarba big+h+na na badz+ra k+ai li
NK011(da)005:246: badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:247: h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata phata kyis sngags kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:248: gdab phur lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas rdzas
NK011(da)005:249: kyi phur bu ye shes kyi khro bo chen po'i
NK011(da)005:250: rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK011(da)005:252: de nas snying por bzlas pa'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)005:253: khams gsum ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:254: sgrub pa'i ye shes tshon gang ba //
NK011(da)005:255: gsang ba sngags kyis bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:256: thugs la 'bar ba'i srog kyang shar //
NK011(da)005:257: dus kun rgyun du bzla dgongs pas //
NK011(da)005:258: snying po 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:262: man ngag gi snying po 'di byin te dbang bskur
NK011(da)005:263: bar de ring phan chad bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung
NK011(da)005:264: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:267: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:268: tsham rngams gzi byin glog ltar 'gyu //
NK011(da)005:269: nyes byed gsum gyi khams bsreg phyir //
NK011(da)005:270: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:271: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:272: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru sta na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:273: de nas phur bu tho ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:274: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)005:275: khro bo 'bar ba'i gtun tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)005:276: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:277: phur bu tho ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:278: thams cad sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:279: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya mu sti h+aum /
NK011(da)005:281: phur bu tho ba 'di lag tu byin zhing dbar
NK011(da)005:282: bskur bas dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad nas zhi
NK011(da)005:283: zhing rnam par shes pa mi gnas pa'i mya ngan
NK011(da)005:284: las 'das pa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings su
NK011(da)005:285: sgrol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:286: de nas phur bu 'debs pa'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)005:287: bdag dang lag pa mchog rnams kyis //
NK011(da)005:288: rab tu 'dril te gsor byas nas //
NK011(da)005:289: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:291: pa ra bi t+wa na h+aum pa ra bid+ya ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:293: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:295: t+r+aa sa ya t+r+aa sa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:296: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:297: sh+ai g+h+ram a na ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:298: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:299: a be sha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:300: b+han+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:302: m+aa ra ya phata a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:303: phur bu 'di lag tu byin nas dbang bskur bas
NK011(da)005:304: dug gsum gyis bskyed pa'i dgra bgegs rnams rdul phran
NK011(da)005:305: bzhin du brlag nas sgrol zhing tshar gcod pa'i mthu
NK011(da)005:306: stobs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK011(da)005:307: cig / ces 'debs phur lag tu sbyin no //
NK011(da)005:308: de nas dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK011(da)005:309: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)005:310: byang chub sems ni mngon du bstan //
NK011(da)005:311: khams gsum ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:312: dbu la rigs lnga'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:313: bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK011(da)005:314: badz+ra ak+sho b+h+ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK011(da)005:315: rat+na sam+b+ha ba a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK011(da)005:316: pad+ma de ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih a mo g+ha sid+d+hi karma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:317: rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis slob ma khyod la
NK011(da)005:318: dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas phung po lnga dang
NK011(da)005:319: dug lnga gnas su dag nas rigs lnga ye shes
NK011(da)005:320: lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:321: de nas cod pan gyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:322: bdag cag nyes pa'i skyon bral zhing //
NK011(da)005:323: 'khor ba'i chos kyis ma gos pa'i //
NK011(da)005:324: ye shes lnga yi cod pan gyis //
NK011(da)005:325: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK011(da)005:326: badz+ra pa ra lam pa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih
NK011(da)005:327: bu khyod la le brgan gyi dbang bskur bas khams
NK011(da)005:328: gsum chos kyi rgyal por gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:329: mthing ga'i dbang bskur bas khams gsum gyi gdug pa
NK011(da)005:330: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK011(da)005:331: cig / phreng ba'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:333: byang chub mchog rnams rtogs pa'i rgyan //
NK011(da)005:334: mi 'jigs chos dang dpe byad mtshan //
NK011(da)005:335: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:336: badz+ra na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aa le tram /
NK011(da)005:337: rigs kyi bu khyod la rin po che'i phreng ba'i
NK011(da)005:338: dbang bskur bas mi brjed pa'i gzungs dang sangs rgyas
NK011(da)005:339: kyi che ba'i yon tan thams cad la dbang ba'i
NK011(da)005:340: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:341: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:343: dri chen dang ni byang chub sems //
NK011(da)005:344: m+aam sa rak+ta dri chu lnga //
NK011(da)005:345: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:346: rtogs sbyongs bdud rtsi'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:347: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum a /
NK011(da)005:348: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i dbang bskur bas ye shes
NK011(da)005:349: lnga'i don rtogs nas rigs lnga'i dngos grub thob ste
NK011(da)005:350: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga'i
NK011(da)005:351: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:354: mi dang ba lang rta sha dang //
NK011(da)005:355: bya khyi la sogs sha rnams kyi //
NK011(da)005:356: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:357: rig 'dzin gtso bor dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:358: ha m+aam sa a yu she h+aum a /
NK011(da)005:359: rigs kyi bu khyod la sha lnga'i dbang bskur bas
NK011(da)005:360: 'byung ba lnga gnas su dag nas rigs kyi yum
NK011(da)005:361: lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:362: de nas gsang ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:363: bkra shis mtshan ldan gsang ba'i yum //
NK011(da)005:364: bu mo lo grangs nyi shu pa //
NK011(da)005:365: chas byas rgyan ldan bla ma la //
NK011(da)005:366: yon dang bcas te dbul bar bya //
NK011(da)005:367: bla mas gdams ngag don bshad de //
NK011(da)005:368: dam tshig phog la dkyil 'khor gzhug /
NK011(da)005:369: byin rlabasadabanga ni bskur bya ste //
NK011(da)005:371: de yi lus ni gnas bcu la //
NK011(da)005:372: khro mo bcu yi dkyil 'khor bkod //
NK011(da)005:373: b+ha ga pad+mara byin brlabs am //
NK011(da)005:374: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur //
NK011(da)005:375: gsal ba'i gnas bcu khro bo'i bcu //
NK011(da)005:376: gsang gnas rdo rje'i rtse mor //
NK011(da)005:377: dzahh+aum bam hohs bsdu ba bya /
NK011(da)005:378: bsdu dang brgyud dang phab pa las //
NK011(da)005:379: spro bsdu sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK011(da)005:380: ba spu'i bu gar thim pa las //
NK011(da)005:381: yab yum bde ba'i ngang du gsal //
NK011(da)005:382: slob mas tshig 'dis gsol ba gdab /
NK011(da)005:383: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK011(da)005:384: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)005:385: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)005:386: sku yi dbyig nas bdag bskyed cig /
NK011(da)005:387: bla mas blob ma byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)005:388: yab yum gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK011(da)005:389: slob ma'i rgyud la spros byas pas //
NK011(da)005:390: nye bar len pa'i phung po sbyangs //
NK011(da)005:391: 'od zhu h+aum gyur thugs kar bsdu //
NK011(da)005:392: srog dbugs brgyud de klad rgyas su //
NK011(da)005:393: phyugs nas sgal tshigs brgyud pa las //
NK011(da)005:394: mkha' la byang sems thig ler gsal //
NK011(da)005:395: de la yi ge h+aum du gyur //
NK011(da)005:396: de las rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed //
NK011(da)005:397: tshig gsum gong dang 'dra ba las //
NK011(da)005:399: sku yi dbyibs nas bskyed par bya'o //
NK011(da)005:400: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku ma r+aa dzah +aahh+aum /
NK011(da)005:401: nyi ma'i gdan la bzhag nas ni //
NK011(da)005:402: yab yum sbyor ba dngos su brtsams //
NK011(da)005:403: byang sems phab ste me long blangs //
NK011(da)005:404: yig 'bru gsum du byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)005:405: sbom po dang ni dbang mo rtser //
NK011(da)005:406: nyi zla gsal bas blangs bya te //
NK011(da)005:407: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK011(da)005:408: a mri ta sbyar la b+han+d+ha mtshan dang ldan par
NK011(da)005:409: blugs la bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs /
NK011(da)005:410: sman gsos che ba'i yon tan brjod //
NK011(da)005:411: sman gyi mchod pa rgyas par bya //
NK011(da)005:412: dang por bdag nyid dngos grub blangs //
NK011(da)005:413: de nas slob mar dbang bskur te //
NK011(da)005:415: rnam rtog bdud 'joms sman mchog bdud rtsi 'di //
NK011(da)005:416: dus gsum sangs rgyas mnyes pa'i mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)005:417: thig le dbyings nas rang byung ye shes shar //
NK011(da)005:418: skye 'chi med pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:419: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kun+da li sid+d+hi h+aum h+r+aihth+aah h+aum /
NK011(da)005:420: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)005:421: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)005:422: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK011(da)005:423: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:424: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK011(da)005:426: e ma ho nga ni rang byung ba'i //
NK011(da)005:427: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK011(da)005:429: gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyi //
NK011(da)005:430: de ring khyod la dngos grub sbyin //
NK011(da)005:431: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aahh+aum a yu she sid+d+hi h+aum a /
NK011(da)005:432: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas thabs dang shes
NK011(da)005:433: rab kyi dbang thob ste 'khor ba'i chos mya ngan
NK011(da)005:434: las 'das te dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku gsung
NK011(da)005:435: thugs kyi dngos grub kyi dbyig thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)005:437: ye shes khro bo h+aum k+aa ra //
NK011(da)005:438: sgra 'byin ma dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK011(da)005:439: gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyis //
NK011(da)005:440: spyi bo nas ni dbang bskur zhing //
NK011(da)005:441: lce yi steng du bzhag pa yis //
NK011(da)005:442: h+aum chen yab yum dngos grub sbyin //
NK011(da)005:443: khro bcu yab yum des 'gres so //
NK011(da)005:445: 'di ni rdo rje ming gi dbang //
NK011(da)005:446: mtshan mchog 'di yi dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:447: sangs rgyas zhing du grags pa'i dbang //
NK011(da)005:449: sh+r+ai badz+ra n+aa ma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah de nas
NK011(da)005:450: tshogs byin gyis brlabs nas zhal zas rnams gsar te
NK011(da)005:451: / 'jig rten 'di na srid pa'i zhal zas rnams //
NK011(da)005:452: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi gter //
NK011(da)005:453: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)005:454: yid bzhin 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:455: gu na pany+tsa a yu she h+aum a /
NK011(da)005:456: zhal zas kyi dbang bskur bas 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK011(da)005:457: mi zad pa'i gter la dbang thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)005:458: / de ltar zhal zas kyis dbang bskur zin pa dang /
NK011(da)005:459: slob mas slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang srung ma rnams rgyas par mchod do //
NK011(da)005:460: de nas dza gad kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:461: b+han+d+hara dza gad stsal la byin gyis brlabs te /
NK011(da)005:463: dza gad dpa' bo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)005:464: yon tan yum gyi byin brlabs pas //
NK011(da)005:465: stong khams kun gyi bcud bsdus nas //
NK011(da)005:466: thugs rje nus pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:467: a ti pra ti sa ma ma ki ri si ti h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsaa /
NK011(da)005:471: de nas pham phab kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:472: chogs kyi lhag ma rnams bsdus la /
NK011(da)005:474: rgyal ba mchod nas dam skong zhig /
NK011(da)005:475: mchod pa phul bas bgegs zhi nas //
NK011(da)005:476: pham phab longs spyod bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK011(da)005:477: rnal 'byor longs spyod rgyas par shog /
NK011(da)005:478: sarba p+au dza karma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:481: zla gam dmar po rdo rje'i dbang gi tshe //
NK011(da)005:482: gzhan gyis mi dpog khams gsum kun las rgyal //
NK011(da)005:483: lha mo dmar mo rdo rje 'chi med tshe //
NK011(da)005:484: legs pa'i yon tan 'dod pa'i longs spyod rgyas //
NK011(da)005:485: mi 'gyur 'chi med tshe lo stong phrag dang //
NK011(da)005:486: rang nyid gang 'dod phung po rdo rje'i tshe //
NK011(da)005:487: a yu dmar po yongs su 'gyur med pa //
NK011(da)005:488: mi 'phrog des pa'i tshe mchog gang yin pa //
NK011(da)005:489: yun ring dus nas bsnyen cing bsgrub bsgrubs nas //
NK011(da)005:490: rdo rje tshe yi dbang mchog gang yin pa //
NK011(da)005:491: rigs kyi bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:492: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu h+ya a
NK011(da)005:493: yu dz+ny+aa na bin+d+hu yu tsi shwa ra swa b+h+aa
NK011(da)005:495: tshe bum gyi dbang bskur bas bcom ldan 'das mgon
NK011(da)005:496: po tshe dpag med kyi sid+d+hi thob nas skye shi
NK011(da)005:497: med pa rdo rje tshe'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)005:498: / de nas rnal 'byor ba rnams dbang rim par sbyar ba 'di skad do //
NK011(da)005:499: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)005:500: dam rdzas gnyan po mngon bkram nas //
NK011(da)005:501: rdo rje bdag po dngos grub bdag po yi //
NK011(da)005:502: dbang dang dngos grub rdzas mchog rnams //
NK011(da)005:503: gang zhig dngos grub 'dod pa nga las longs //
NK011(da)005:504: bu mchog rnams kyis dngos grub thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:505: las dang sgrub pa'i dbang dang byin brlabs rnams //
NK011(da)005:506: sgrub mchog rnams kyi rim bzhin thob gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:507: da ni b+han+d+ha'i dbang bskur ba 'di skad do //
NK011(da)005:508: thugs rje dbang mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK011(da)005:509: ta kri ta 'bar tshogs bcas pa ma lus kun //
NK011(da)005:510: snod bcud dbang bskur dbang rdzas 'dis //
NK011(da)005:511: mu stegs gnod sbyin thod thogs dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)005:512: dpal gyi snod zhal lcang lo 'khyil ba 'dis //
NK011(da)005:513: mkha' 'gro 'bar ba rol par byin brlabs la //
NK011(da)005:514: dpa' bo mgo la rnam shes sna tshogs pas //
NK011(da)005:515: ye shes rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos grub 'di byin no //
NK011(da)005:516: ka p+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa sarba ma tra /
NK011(da)005:517: b+han+d+ha 'phrul gyi zhal bus dbang bskur bas spang len
NK011(da)005:518: byed pa'i bya ba lhun gyis rdzogs te dur khrod
NK011(da)005:519: chen po'i gnas su sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor byin gyis
NK011(da)005:520: brlabs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:521: de nas chas brgyad kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:524: zhing lpags rtag tu g.yogs pa dur khrod bdag /
NK011(da)005:525: g.yang gzhi tshigs su sdud pas sku la bcings //
NK011(da)005:526: 'khor ba ma spangs gnas su dag pa yi //
NK011(da)005:527: dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:528: zhing chen rlon pa thabs la mkhas pa yis //
NK011(da)005:529: 'khor ba'i gnas na yongs su rgyal bar shog /
NK011(da)005:533: glang chen ko rlon brjid du che ba yi //
NK011(da)005:534: gti mug ma lus gnas su dag pa'i rgyan //
NK011(da)005:535: na baza'i rgyan gyis sku la mnga' gsol zhing //
NK011(da)005:536: thabs kyi ko rlon rgyan gyi dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)005:537: gang la dbang mchog 'di yi dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:538: stobs kyi rgyal po'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:539: ma dar ta sa sha ta h+aum /
NK011(da)005:540: stag gi sham thabs kyi dbang /
NK011(da)005:542: zhe sdang drag po stag gi sham thabs 'di //
NK011(da)005:543: stag lpags sham thabs dpa' bar ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)005:544: sug ldob 'doms su bsnol ba phyi nang gsang ba gcig /
NK011(da)005:545: phrag dog gnas 'joms stag lpags dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:546: zhe sdang gnas 'joms phrag dog gnas 'joms pa'i //
NK011(da)005:547: dbang mchog dam pa khyod kyis thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:548: badz+ra bya kri tsarma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum a /
NK011(da)005:550: thod sbrul mnyen lcug 'jigs byed rgyan du che //
NK011(da)005:551: sbrul nag stong gis brgyan pa'i rngams brjid can //
NK011(da)005:552: sku la mchod phyir sku yi gnas lngar 'khril //
NK011(da)005:553: dug lnga gnas lnga gnas su 'dul ba'i thabs su ston //
NK011(da)005:554: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem zhe sdang drag po 'joms //
NK011(da)005:555: rdzu 'phrul shugs kyis klu brgyad dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)005:556: gti mug 'dul ba'i dbang phyug yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:557: sbrul nag stong gi chun po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:558: zhe sdang 'bar ba gnas dag nas //
NK011(da)005:559: thabs mkhas rgyal po mnyes pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:560: n+aa ga ra tsa hu lu hu lu h+aum /
NK011(da)005:562: dung chen phreng ba dbang po lnga dang ldan //
NK011(da)005:563: sku gsum tshul 'chang skam po ra ri'i tshul //
NK011(da)005:564: 'khor ba gsum sdud thabs kyi phreng bas brgyan //
NK011(da)005:565: khams gsum dbang sdud thod phreng dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:566: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)005:567: pad+ma b+han+d+ha ka p+aa la ha sta h+aum /
NK011(da)005:570: 'bar ba'i phreng ba ye shes me ri ldan //
NK011(da)005:571: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams nyon mongs dug bsregs pa //
NK011(da)005:572: bskal pa me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na gnas //
NK011(da)005:573: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcu'i mun nag sel //
NK011(da)005:574: bskal pa me ri 'bar ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:575: bar chad bgegs kyi rtog pas mi tshugs shing //
NK011(da)005:576: mtshan ma 'dzin rtog bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:577: badz+ra dz+wa la badz+ra dz+wa la ram ram h+aum /
NK011(da)005:578: byug pa rtsi gsum gyi dbang /
NK011(da)005:579: rak+ta'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba dbang du sdud par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:580: thal chen gyi dbang bskur bas 'di dang phyi ma
NK011(da)005:581: gnyis su dur khrod kyi rdzas la longs spyod cing
NK011(da)005:582: dngos grub rnam gnyis 'thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK011(da)005:583: gyur cig / zhag gi zo ris kyi dbang bskur
NK011(da)005:584: bas ma mo dbang phyug ma la sogs pa rtag
NK011(da)005:585: tu mi 'bral zhing bsrung ba dang skyong ba'i dbang
NK011(da)005:588: chos kyi dbyings nyid mi 'gyur rang snang ba //
NK011(da)005:589: ye shes lnga ldan thugs mtshan kun gyi mchog /
NK011(da)005:590: 'dzin pa'i rgyal po rdo rje thugs mtshan 'dis //
NK011(da)005:591: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:593: rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas 'du 'bral skye shi med
NK011(da)005:594: par g.yung drung tshe'i dngos grub dang sngags 'chang rgyal
NK011(da)005:595: po rdo rje 'dzin gyi gral thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)005:597: thugs mchog rtogs pa rig pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)005:598: mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la spyod //
NK011(da)005:599: thabs la mkhas pa sprul pa'i sras //
NK011(da)005:601: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:602: pradz+ny+aa pa ra yo gi du badz+ra tig na g+han+di /
NK011(da)005:604: dus mtha' med par sgrogs pa chos kyi rnga //
NK011(da)005:605: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa chos kyi sgra //
NK011(da)005:606: thugs dam yongs su bskang ba'i rdzas mchog 'dis //
NK011(da)005:607: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:608: ma ka ra sa ya h+aum /
NK011(da)005:609: sgrub pa po ming 'di zhes bya ba la rnga'i
NK011(da)005:610: dbang bskur bas dbyings kyi dngos grub thob ste 'jig
NK011(da)005:611: rten thams cad du chos kyi sgra chen po sgrogs
NK011(da)005:612: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:614: ral pa kham nag 'khyil ba chen po 'di //
NK011(da)005:615: dbang drag mthar phyin drag shul sprul pa 'phro //
NK011(da)005:616: sku mchog mthing nag nam mkha'i rgyan bzhes pas //
NK011(da)005:617: yon tan rgyas shing phrin las 'grub par bstan //
NK011(da)005:618: 'khor ba ma spangs ral pa'i rgyan chen 'dis //
NK011(da)005:619: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:620: ma h+aa bi du bi sha ka sid+d+hi hoh mar me'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:621: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i bag chags bsal ba dang //
NK011(da)005:622: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa 'joms pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:623: ye shes 'od ldan gsal ba'i mar me 'dis //
NK011(da)005:624: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:625: ram ha myi ti bam ma h+aa ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)005:626: mar me'i dbang bskur bas rnam rtog mi mnga' cir
NK011(da)005:627: yang sa ler mkhyen pa'i sa thob nas ye shes
NK011(da)005:628: kyi mes bag chags thams cad bsreg pa'i dbang dang
NK011(da)005:630: byug bdug brab pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)005:632: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chags pa'i bdag nyid ni //
NK011(da)005:633: dgra bgegs thams cad dbang du sdud par byed //
NK011(da)005:634: chags pa'i thugs rjes 'khor ba mi gtong ba //
NK011(da)005:635: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:636: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+d+ha la h+aum /
NK011(da)005:638: gu gul gyi dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)005:639: gu gul sbyar ba'i rdzas mchog dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)005:640: sdang ba'i dgra bo lha dang phral ba dang //
NK011(da)005:641: gnod pa'i bgegs ni myos shing bsub par byed //
NK011(da)005:642: srid gsum dbang du bsdud pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)005:643: ma gul ta la ta la a ti pri h+aum phataha b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)005:644: yungs kar rgyal po'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)005:645: yungs dkar rgyal po'i rdzas mchog dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)005:646: gser mdog gzigs 'phags rdo rje 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK011(da)005:647: dgra bgegs ma lus rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)005:648: khams gsum sgrol ba'i bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)005:649: pe ta li man+d+ha la rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)005:651: dbang rdzas bsdus la snying gar bzhag la /
NK011(da)005:653: tshe yi snying po rgyud gsum po //
NK011(da)005:654: srog gi snying po gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)005:655: skye shi med pa byang chub sems //
NK011(da)005:656: sku gsum sku ste sku la thim //
NK011(da)005:657: gsung gsum gsung ste gsung la thim //
NK011(da)005:658: thugs gsum thugs te thugs la thim //
NK011(da)005:659: sku gsung thugs la rab tu thim //
NK011(da)005:660: a yu pha la sid+d+hi sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK011(da)005:662: a be sha ya a a /
NK011(da)005:664: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyi dngos grub kyi zhal zas tsho bzhir bgos la bla ma mchod /
NK011(da)005:667: mched lcam yongs la sbyin no //
NK011(da)005:672: ma dag pa bzod par gsol /
NK011(da)005:676: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin bya'o //
NK011(da)005:677: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i dbang gi chog khrigs rdzogs so //
NK011(da)005:679: // dge ba 'di yis mnyam med gter bdag gling //
NK011(da)005:680: zag med thugs kyi dgongs pa yongs rdzogs shing //
NK011(da)005:681: rnying bstan mi nyams dar zhing rgyas pa yi //
NK011(da)005:682: rtsa lag srog gi ka bar 'di gyur cig /
NK011(da)005:685: // rgyal dang de sras rig pa 'dzin rnams kyi //
NK011(da)005:686: ring lugs snga 'gyur 'o ma'i rgya mtsho las //
NK011(da)005:687: phrin chog zhun mar snying po bsdus pa 'dis //
NK011(da)005:688: gzhan la phan pa mtha' yas 'grub gyur cig /
